# Project: <PROJECT_NAME>

## Stack
- <e.g., TypeScript, Next.js, Tailwind, Postgres>

## Conventions
- Use conventional commits (feat:, fix:, chore:, docs:)
- Prefer named exports over default exports
- Use async/await over .then() chains
- Colocate tests next to source files (*.test.ts)
- No any types — use unknown + type narrowing if needed

## Code Style
- Concise over verbose — no unnecessary abstractions
- Functions over classes unless state is genuinely needed
- Early returns over nested conditionals
- Descriptive variable names — no abbreviations except well-known ones (id, url, db)

## File Structure
- `src/` — application source
- `tests/` — integration/e2e tests
- `scripts/` — build and deploy helpers

